  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CommissionedEmployee, Employee

    final class LibraryAssociate
extends LibraryEmployee
implements CommissionedEmployee
    Sales associates are store employees who also receive a commission on their sales. The commission is a percentage of their current sales, individual sales associates may receive different percentages of their sales in commission.
    Author:
    Chris Turner
